<div id="review_21573953" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/21573953" />
    <a title="Jeff" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/166787-jeff"><img alt="Jeff" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1222352072p2/166787.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/21573953?book_show_action=true">May 04, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jeff" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jeff" href="/user/show/166787-jeff">Jeff</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer21573953" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9514357925236284395">This book is getting a lot of advance praise and will most certainly be a critical hit. I&apos;m sure many people will adore this book, I am unfortunately not one of those people. The writing is beautiful, the story is ambitious, but I found the book utterly monotonous. I kept reading because I felt I should finish the book, not because I wanted to. </span>
  <span id="freeText9514357925236284395" style="display:none">This book is getting a lot of advance praise and will most certainly be a critical hit. I'm sure many people will adore this book, I am unfortunately not one of those people. The writing is beautiful, the story is ambitious, but I found the book utterly monotonous. I kept reading because I felt I should finish the book, not because I wanted to. </span>
  <a data-text-id="9514357925236284395" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
